  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl83_LabelType\">You can select a magnetic compass for your arcane bond class feature; this compass is nonmagical, but you can later spend 250 gp to upgrade it into a <em>wayfinder</em>. Choosing this trait allows you to upgrade this <em>wayfinder</em> to a variant or unique <em>wayfinder </em>per the normal rules for improving magic items on page 553 of the <em>Pathfinder RPG Core Rulebook</em>. A bonded <em>wayfinder </em>must be held in your hand to grant the benefits of being a bonded object.</span></p>",
